    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Another convenient way to copy the values from src ArrayList to dest Arraylist is as follows:</p>\n\n<pre><code>ArrayList&lt;String&gt; src = new ArrayList&lt;String&gt;();\nsrc.add(\"test string1\");\nsrc.add(\"test string2\");\nArrayList&lt;String&gt; dest= new ArrayList&lt;String&gt;();\ndest.addAll(src);\n</code></pre>\n\n<p>This is actual copying of values and not just copying of reference.</p>\n"
