    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>There is a method <strong>addAll()</strong> which will serve the purpose of copying One ArrayList to another.</p>\n\n<p>For example you have two Array Lists: <em>sourceList</em> and <em>targetList</em>, use below code.</p>\n\n<p><strong>targetList.addAll(sourceList);</strong></p>\n"
